# Profile / Me UI

The **Me** tab is a settings surface — solid cards and list groups, **not** liquid glass metrics.

## Tab shell

Follow `app-shell-ui.mdc`:

- `Scaffold(extendBody: true, backgroundColor: Colors.transparent)`
- `TriftlyAppBarTitle(title: 'Me')` — no glass app bar actions
- Body: `ListView` with `AppSpacing.listBottomInset(context)` bottom padding

## Page structure

```
[ Identity AppCard — avatar, name, sign-in CTA ]
[ SectionHeader — Preferences ]
[ _SettingsGroup AppCard — tiles with dividers ]
[ SectionHeader — Data ]
[ _SettingsGroup … ]
[ SectionHeader — About ]
[ _SettingsGroup … ]
```

| Block | Widget | Notes |
|-------|--------|-------|
| Identity | `AppCard` + `CircleAvatar` | `primaryMuted` avatar bg, `primaryDark` icon |
| Section labels | `SectionHeader` | Page-level only — **not** `SheetSectionHeader` |
| Settings rows | `_SettingsGroup` → `AppCard(padding: zero)` | `Divider` between tiles, `borderLight` / `borderDark` |
| Row tap | `Pressable` + chevron | Title `bodyLarge`, value `bodySmall`, `textTertiary` chevron |

## Settings tile pattern

- One row = title (+ optional trailing value) + `Icons.chevron_right_rounded`
- Horizontal padding `AppSpacing.lg`, vertical **16**
- No switches inline unless the control is the whole row (e.g. future toggles)

## Appearance sheet (`appearance_bottom_sheet.dart`)

Utility sheet — pattern B from `trips-ui-polish.mdc`:

- Open: `AppearanceBottomSheet.show(context)` via `TriftlyBottomSheet.show`
- `SheetScaffold(showCloseButton: false)`
- `SheetSectionHeader(title: 'Appearance', caption: 'Choose a theme')`
- Options in `SheetSoftCard(padding: zero)` with `SheetSoftListDivider` between rows
- Each option: `SheetOptionRow` (icon tile + title/subtitle + checkmark when selected)
- Persist via `ThemeController` / `ThemeScope.of(context)` — **not** `setState` on the page alone

## Sign-in sheet (`sign_in_bottom_sheet.dart`)

Utility sheet chrome with form-style confirm:

- `SheetSectionHeader` + `SheetSoftCard` + `SheetIconFieldRow` / `SheetInlineField`
- `SheetScaffold.swipeForm(compact: true)` + `SwipeToConfirm` (**Slide to sign in** / **Slide to verify**)
- Spacing via `AppSpacing` — no magic numbers

## Default currency sheet (`default_currency_bottom_sheet.dart`)

Same list pattern as appearance:

- `SheetOptionRow` with flag emoji `leading`, code title, symbol · label subtitle
- `SheetSoftListDivider` between rows — **not** `ListTile` / bare `Divider`

## Do not

- Use `SpendGlassShell` or wallet-style heroes on Me
- Use `SheetSectionHeader` on the page body (sheets only)
- Use `FilledButton` for settings navigation — `TextButton` / `Pressable` rows only

